mulx39.title: B.Sc. (Honours) Agriculture Part II – Semester I Practical Examination Notification (2025–26)B.Sc. (Honours) Agriculture Part II – Semester I Practical Examination Notification (2025–26)
mulx39.content:
The practical examinations for B.Sc. (Honours) Agriculture Part II, Semester I for the academic session 2025–26 will be conducted from 15 December 2025 to 26 December 2025. Students are instructed to check the detailed subject-wise schedule given below and appear for the practicals on the respective dates. Batch–A (Roll No. 1–34) will attend from 10:00 AM to 1:00 PM and Batch–B (Roll No. 35 onward) from 2:00 PM to 5:00 PM. All students must report on time with their practical records and follow examination guidelines issued by the college.
